";s:14:"upgrade_notice";s:311:"<h4>1.3</h4>
<p>Version 1.3 has been released with a redesigned Inspiration phase. For more information on this change and others, please visit our blog at https://www.boldgrid.com/boldgrid-1-3-released/ .</p>
