<ul>
<li>Update: JIRA WPB-3292 Updated plugin URI.</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.4.2</h4>
<ul>
<li>Bug fix: JIRA WPB-3161 Fixed auto plugin update.</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.4.1</h4>
<ul>
<li>Bug fix: JIRA WPB-3151 Added check and load before using get<em>plugin</em>data() for updates.</li>
<li>Update: JIRA WPB-3112 Updated wc-gallery: 1.52 => 1.55.</li>
</ul>
<h4>1.4</h4>
<ul>
<li>Bug fix: JIRA WPB-2912 Fixed issue when installing plugins from the Tools Import page.</li>
</ul>
